Deferred tax assets, reference to note 23 shows none.
The total for non‐current assets is 6,569.2 for 1 April 2017 and 7,015.0 for 2 April 2016.
Under the heading Current Assets, the following entries are listed:
Inventories: 758.5, 799.9;
Other financial assets, reference to note 16: 14.5, 19.1;
